                        <interp inst="t18460615-name-967" type="given" value="GEOBOE"></interp>GEOBOE WILD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 94.) I produce a certificate of Smith's former conviction at Newington—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 3<hi rend="italic">rd July</hi>, 1843, <hi rend="italic">and con<lb></lb>fined three months, and whipped</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
